    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40-2018 factor table. Validation results demonstrate that the CFD model predicts the relative hemolysis index within experimental uncertainty across all 5 operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion with margin. The model is accepted as credible for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
