    "modelVersion": "ansys-cfx-hemolysis-2026-q1-build-5",
    "description": "ANSYS CFX solver configuration for centrifugal blood pump hemolysis simulation. SST k-omega turbulence model with curvature correction. Second-order upwind advection scheme. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen-Wurzinger correlation). Rotating reference frame for impeller domain. Medium mesh (4.8M cells) selected based on GCI study."
  },
